[{"Id": 1016411, "EnglishTitle": "Namaz for seeking help from Imam Mahdi (a) on Thursday and Friday night.", "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": "Namaz-e-Isteghasa Imam-e-Mahdi (a) Thursday aur Friday raat mein.", "UrduTitle": "جمعرات اور جمعہ کی شب میں پڑھے جانے والی امام عصر (عج) کی نماز استغاثہ۔", "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016412, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "This same prayer has been mentioned by Sadr ul Islam Hamadani in his invaluable book Takaleef ul Anaam fi Ghaibatil Imam with a different method: He narrates from the authentic Syed, the teacher and Godly cleric, the sage of Samadan, the absolute jurisprudent, Syed Mohammad Hindi Najafi, who narrates from the great cleric Syed Hasan Qazweeni, who narrates from Syed Hasan Shustari - the Imam of congregational prayer who narrates with his authority from Syed Alikhan, the commentator of Sahifa e Sajjadiyya, that: On Thursday night or Friday night, offer two units of prayer beneath the sky and above the roof with bare head and foot, and after offering the prayer bareheaded, say: “YAA HUJJA-TAL QAAE-ME” 595 times (as per its alphabetical numerology). Know that its numerological number is derived by the following method: (10 + 1 + 8 + 3 + 400 + 1 + 30 + 100 + 1 + 1 + 40 = 595) the sum of which is equal to 595. He has said: Keep this act hidden from those who are not worthy of it, because it is one of the secrets which I have tested several times.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Allama Sadr-e-Islaam Hamadani apni giraan-qadr kitaab “Takaaleef-ul-Anaam Fee Ghaibatil Imam” mein is amal ko dusri tarah naql karte hai woh Sayed sanad, Ustaad Aalim Rabbaani , Hakeem aur Faqeeh Zaahed Mohammad Hindi Najafi se woh Buzurg Aalim-e-deen Sayed Hasan Qazweeni se aur woh Sayed Hasan Shustri (Imam-e-Jamaat) se sanad ke saath Sayed Ali Khan (Sahifa-e-Sajjadiya ke Sharah) se naql karte huwe kehte hai keh, Shab-e-Juma aur Roz-e-Juma zer-e-aasmaan (khule aasmaan) chhat par nange sar aur paiyr, 2 rakat namaz (Subh ki tarah) padhe aur uske baad 595 martaba kahe “YAA HUJJA-TAL QAAE-ME” aur yeh is ibaadat ke adad mein aur is tawassul ki taaseer tajurba se saabit hai woh aage kehte hai; “YAA HUJJA-TAL QAAE-ME” ka adad (10 + 1 + 8 + 3 + 400 + 1 + 30 + 100 + 1 + 1 + 40 = 595) hai jo keh majmooa’ 595 hota hai. Yeh amal israar mein se hai iski hifaazat karo ham ne baarhaal is amal ka tajurba kiya hai.", "UrduDescription": "علامہ بزرگوار صدر الاسلا م ھمدانی اپنی عمدہ کتاب تکالیف الانام فی غیبة الامام میں اس عمل کو ایک اور طریقہ سے نقل کیا ہے اس نے سید سند استاد اور عالم ربّانی حکیم فقیہ پرہیزگار سید محمد ہندی نجفی سے اس نے عالم بزرگوار سید حسن قزوینی سے اس نے سید حسین شوشتری امام جماعت سند کے ساتھ سید علی خان سے نقل کیا ہے۔ جو صحیفہ سجادیہ کا شارح ہے کہتاہے کہ شب جمعرات اور جمعہ شب جمعہ آسمان کے نیچے چھت کے اوپر سر برہنہ دو رکعت نماز پڑھتا تھا اس کے بعد ۵۹۵ مرتبہ کہتا تھا یا حجة اللہ سے مجموع عدد وہی عبارت ہوتی ہے اور اس توسل کی تاثیر پر تجربہ ہوا ہے وہ اضافہ کرتاہے کہ عدد یا حجة القائم عبارت ہے ۱۰+ ۱ + ۸+ ۳+ ۱۰۰+ ۱-+ ۳۰ + ۱۰۰ + ۱ + ۴۰) کہ مجموعی طور پر ۵۹۵ ہے یہ ایک خاص عمل میں ہے اس کی حفاظت کی کوشش کریں میں نے بارھا اس عمل کے ساتھ تجربہ کیا ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "A